OL,3,CTeen hid in his mum's attic after
OL,4,Cstabbing 17-year-old in neck at Metro
OL,5,CStation
OL,7,FA teenager has been sentenced after he
OL,8,Fwas found guilty of stabbing a 17-year-
OL,9,Fold boy in the neck at a Metro station
OL,10,Fin South Tyneside.
OL,12,FThe 17-year-old, who cannot be named
OL,13,Fbecause of his age, was found hiding
OL,14,Fin an attic after the attack at
OL,15,FBrockley Whins Metro station on 11
OL,16,FMarch 2024.
OL,18,FThe court heard how he had swung the
OL,19,Fblade at the victim's head and neck,
OL,20,Fcausing a large laceration to his neck
OL,21,Fmillimetres from his main artery.
