OL,7,FThe victim only realised he had been
OL,8,Fstabbed when he saw he was covered in
OL,9,Fblood and bleeding profusely.
OL,11,FThe victim's mother was called and
OL,12,Fused a towel to stem the bleeding.
OL,14,FThe defendant was identified by CCTV
OL,15,Fpictures and was later found hiding in
OL,16,Fthe attic of his mother's house.
OL,18,FHe was found guilty of Grievous Bodily
OL,19,FHarm following a four-day trial at
OL,20,FNewcastle Crown Court in July.
