OL,7,FAt a sentencing hearing at the same
OL,8,Fcourt on Wednesday 11 September, he
OL,9,Fwas sentenced to two years and three
OL,10,Fmonths in a Young Offenders Institute.
OL,12,FInvestigating officer DC Colin Dore of
OL,13,FBritish Transport Police said: "It is
OL,14,Fby sheer good fortune and the
OL,15,Fexpertise of medics that the victim
OL,16,Fdid not die from the injuries he
OL,17,Fsustained in this brutal attack.
